               <title>6 ADVERSE REACTIONS</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>No adverse reactions have been reported for Sodium Fluoride F 18 Injection based on a review of the published literature, publicly available reference sources, and adverse drug reaction reporting systems.  However, the completeness of these sources is not known.</paragraph>
               </text>
